name: T-shirt
description:
Grafitti meets block print- Zac's stencils were changed into blocks and discharged and printed across the pure cotton of this T-shirt, just like painting on a wall.

Just like walls, this T-shirt's colour will change with time- cold wash separately and dry in shade.

Size small -unisex design.

FREE SHIPPING from our workshop

Irregularities in print, weave, embroidery and color are inherent characteristics of hand crafted textiles.
